{"tid":261761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣，好驚訓覺失去意識","createTime":"2017-05-28T16:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T14:17:15.000Z","uid":76695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"046fd56fa99d529645caa27b2b09e4f4a8f340ec","tid":261761,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:52:02.000Z","msg":"真心post<br />\n其實我自幾年前 就已經有去諗<br />\n訓覺之後既我係咪真係訓覺教<br />\n<br />\n講緊既 唔係講緊睡眠質素個啲<br />\n而係我控制唔到自己身體<br />\n其實發生緊咩事我係真係一無所知<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度<br />\n可能你地會話<br />\n超 訓覺咪訓覺囉<br />\n係到諗咁多都無用xxxxxxxx...<br />\n<br />\n但係對於一個被呢個問題纏繞緊好耐既人來講<br />\n解決唔到先係最差既感覺<br />\n<br />\n諗左好耐好唔好post出來<br />\n但係都想知有無比呢樣野困擾住既巴絲<br />\n我想正視呢個問題<br />\n所以大家不妨可以分享一下比小弟聽(如果有)<br />\n<br />\n最後見到網上面有一句真係好精警<br />\n&lsquo;比失眠更可怕既係害怕失眠&rsquo;<br />\n其實我可能好似網上咁講，對訓覺有恐懼<br />\n而呢個問題都係間中先出現<br />\n只係今次選擇開post<br />\n想知道大家有無相似既問題煩緊"},{"pid":"24b84d2bb3bc3e092d10d79b54818fd8bb1dff34","tid":261761,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:59:15.000Z","msg":"驚瞓瞓下猝死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688126d7d9a8293881fab4ab412e89323ec2ba2f","tid":261761,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲我訓先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓到固然好<br />\n訓唔到睇下有冇人覆再討論<br />\n冇人睇就由得佢沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b759d95b1d805cc557cded92babeacef148195","tid":261761,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚瞓瞓下猝死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4f3a019e4f7dc15e45e1e1bf6e21f4d35c6266","tid":261761,"uid":76695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚瞓瞓下猝死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲你係晚晚都係咁諗定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632c296610544fa10035a68906ea37821a418b6d","tid":261761,"uid":52593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:07:47.000Z","msg":"好想訓訓下教死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ebd4c656dcdf62bc0da67500eddd07edec38c9","tid":261761,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>驚瞓瞓下猝死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲你係晚晚都係咁諗定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n越夜瞓越驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b60a4167d44de77a9de685b80f7a7e99fac131","tid":261761,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想訓訓下教死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想無痛咁死左 生存好大壓力"},{"pid":"d7afbf8d314819967423793735debd6a28e4d8cb","tid":261761,"uid":4,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"好想一睡不起"},{"pid":"588b2be6d274f59557642d86d046448b0d6e12f9","tid":261761,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19005c6f434935af17906b859e7cd6724a8425d","tid":261761,"uid":10848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:57:23.000Z","msg":"之前焦慮症發作時就會咁諗，巴打你有無考慮過係咪有d情緒問題所以令你有咁既諗法？"},{"pid":"2058e3d5fe0eac0032ff991560d930a76508bc63","tid":261761,"uid":71389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T21:00:47.000Z","msg":"不如問下自己點解咁驚死"},{"pid":"8f1970a8a49b4f77ca8b027fd2fff8d577f31758"